Package: type
Title: Runtime Type Validation for Functions and Objects
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(
      "Ethan", "Sansom", 
      email = "ethan.sansom29@gmail.com", 
      role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0000-1573-0186")
    )
Description: Provides a lightweight type system for 'R'. Types are represented as composable sets of predicates which a valid object must satisfy. Variables may be declared with a type, which is checked everytime the variable is assigned to. Additionally, function arguments and return values may be annotated with a type, which is validated each time the function is called.
